143
00:12:07,420 --> 00:12:10,060
not just about the painting when it was painted,

144
00:12:10,060 --> 00:12:14,740
but the the life of the painting, that it's travelled.

145
00:12:16,510 --> 00:12:18,730
You know, hundreds of miles.

146
00:12:18,730 --> 00:12:20,110
It's been in hiding.

